OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775369052
OL,3,CRail delays and yellow wind warnings
OL,4,Cas Storm Dave due to ease on Easter
OL,5,CSunday
OL,7,FStorm Dave caused road closures and
OL,8,Ftrain disruptions across the UK on
OL,9,FEaster Sunday morning.
OL,11,FAn amber wind alert for parts of
OL,12,Fnorthern England, north-west Wales and
OL,13,Fsouthern Scotland was lifted at 3am.
OL,15,FTwo yellow wind alerts remain in place
OL,16,Funtil noon for parts of northern
OL,17,FEngland and Scotland, while a third
OL,18,Falert for Wales will lift at 7am.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
