FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775369052
OL,3,CRail delays and yellow wind warnings
OL,4,Cas Storm Dave due to ease on Easter
OL,5,CSunday
OL,7,FThe Met Office's forecast for Easter
OL,8,FSunday said: "Storm Dave will clear
OL,9,Faway to the northeast... leaving
OL,10,Fsunshine and showers across the UK for
OL,11,FEaster Sunday. The showers look
OL,12,Fparticularly heavy and blustery in the
OL,13,Fnorth."
OL,15,FBut before the severe weather warning
OL,16,Fis lifted, the Met Office said that
OL,17,F"severe gales" were expected across
OL,18,Fcentral and northern areas of the
OL,19,Fcountry in the early hours of Sunday.
OL,26,@pD@NOUuD@GO]yD@AOUyD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
