OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775369052
OL,3,CRail delays and yellow wind warnings
OL,4,Cas Storm Dave due to ease on Easter
OL,5,CSunday
OL,7,FIn the early hours of Sunday, Traffic
OL,8,FScotland warned that several major
OL,9,Fbridges had restrictions in place due
OL,10,Fto strong winds, including the
OL,11,FQueensferry Crossing on the M90, which
OL,12,Fconnects Edinburgh with Fife and the
OL,13,Fnearby Forth Road Bridge on the A9000.
OL,15,FThe Humber Bridge in Yorkshire was
OL,16,Fclosed in both directions to high-
OL,17,Fsided and vulnerable vehicles early on
OL,18,FSunday due to strong winds, National
OL,19,FHighways reported.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775369052
OL,3,CRail delays and yellow wind warnings
OL,4,Cas Storm Dave due to ease on Easter
OL,5,CSunday
OL,7,FElsewhere, ScotRail confirmed
OL,8,Femergency speed restrictions would be
OL,9,Fimplemented across parts of its
OL,10,Fnetwork, resulting in longer travel
OL,11,Ftimes.
OL,13,FIn England's north, Network Rail
OL,14,FManchester announced rail replacement
OL,15,Fbus services would run between
OL,16,FManchester Picadilly and Chester due
OL,17,Fto overnight weather conditions.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
