FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775369052
OL,3,CRail delays and yellow wind warnings
OL,4,Cas Storm Dave due to ease on Easter
OL,5,CSunday
OL,7,FAs of 6am on Sunday, there were four
OL,8,Fcoastal flood warnings and 32 flood
OL,9,Falerts across England, with eight
OL,10,Fcoastal flood alerts in Wales.
OL,12,FThe Energy Networks Association (ENA)
OL,13,F` which represents electricity network
OL,14,Foperators ` warned of potential power
OL,15,Fcuts and issued safety advice
OL,16,Ffollowing the weather warnings.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
