FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1775369052
OL,3,CRail delays and yellow wind warnings
OL,4,Cas Storm Dave due to ease on Easter
OL,5,CSunday
OL,7,FIt said in a statement on Saturday:
OL,8,F"The storm has the potential to affect
OL,9,Flocal power infrastructure, increasing
OL,10,Fthe risk of a power cut and fallen
OL,11,Fpower lines.
OL,13,F"Network operators are increasing
OL,14,Fstaffing for operational teams, and
OL,15,Fmoving spare equipment to where the
OL,16,Fweather is expected to be most
OL,17,Fdisruptive, so it's ready to use if
OL,18,Fneeded."
